<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,151,1293]" pageId="11" pageNumber="530">
Coloration (in alcohol; 
<figureCitation box="[462,527,151,176]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="9.[151,250,1930,1952]" captionTargetBox="[217,1400,218,1908]" captionTargetId="figure@9.[181,1404,193,1917]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURE 4. Lankanectes pera sp. nov., SVL 68.69 mm, DZ1307 (A–D), in preservation. (A) ventral view; (B) right ventral foot; (C) ventral view of the head; (D) lateral view. Lankanectes corrugatus, SVL 55.28 mm, DZ1396 (E–H), in preservation. (A) ventral view; (B) right ventral foot; (C) ventral view of the head; (D) lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1460266/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="530">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
